channel.title: Ventus - Be Ready
channel.description:
[CENTER][IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/2csf5gg.png[/img] Hello, welcome to Ventus. Ever since I became familiar with RuneScape private servers, I've always wanted to make a Pk server. I have tried and I have failed. My last project [URL=http://www.moparisthebest.com/smf/index.php/topic,625161.0.html]Lost Legacy[/URL] was suppose to be something unique, something different. Unfortunately the server was released without my permission which did not allow me to fully finish. I decided that this would be my last project. This server will entirely be Pk'ing based. There will be tons of unique content never seen before on a Pk server. Most Pk private servers you see today are the same thing. There is nothing unique. However we will change that. We will make this something you look forward to play. This will be something that will change history. [size=14pt]Development Team:[/size] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/l3QjY.gif[/img] Play Boy - Server/Client Developer [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/l3QjY.gif[/img] Frost Bit3 - Server/Client Developer [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/l3QjY.gif[/img] AHMG DARIUS - Client Developer Goaliath - GFX [size=14pt]Features:[/size]
*Fully Working Bank Tabs *Bounty Hunter *PvP Drops *100% Ancient Curses *100% All Special Weapons *Unique Clan Chat System
[size=14pt]Media:[/size] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ftGKOobMflA[/youtube] [youtube]http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=x7N9faVhjRE[/youtube] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/mmuecp.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/Q3dJKPB.gif?1[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/35lg8l4.png[/img] [IMG]http://i49.tinypic.com/20jssja.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/52l553.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/bfo1gg.png[/img] [IMG]http://i48.tinypic.com/4sf8uq.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/ojgoww.png[/img] [IMG]http://i50.tinypic.com/351iusy.png[/img] [IMG]http://i.imgur.com/GbCO4hW.png[/img] [size=14pt]Logs:[/size] Play Boy's Logs: [url=http://pastebin.com/xxNfmywH]http://pastebin.com/xxNfmywH[/url] [size=14pt]Credits:[/size] Frostbit3 Intrum 'Jerba Jason Meerster Technotik iQuality Eyfia [/CENTER]
